data.description:
Welcome to this enchanting home nestled in the highly sought-after area of Avondale. This turnkey residence welcomes you with an array of modern updates, ensuring a seamless transition into your new haven.Step into the expansive living room flooded with natural light, where the focal point is a charming double-sided fireplace, connecting seamlessly with the den on the other side. Beyond the den, discover the added luxury of a spacious 4-seasons room, providing an ideal retreat for relaxation or entertainment. The kitchen boasts abundant storage, showcasing recent enhancements such as fresh paint, new flooring, upgraded countertops, hardware, and beautifully painted cabinets.The bedrooms are not only tastefully painted but also offer generous amounts of closet space,. All three bathrooms have undergone thoughtful updates, including new flooring. If the den and 4-seasons room leave you craving even more space, venture downstairs to the updated family room, complete with additional storage options and a second fireplace. This home, surprisingly spacious beyond its exterior, invites you to explore its many offerings.
 
Don't miss the opportunity to experience the true essence of this home—schedule a viewing today
